title: Garmin MapSource European City Select 4.00
description:
This torrent contains image files of two discs which came with Garmin Navtalk GSM phone. It contains Garmin MapSource European City Select 4.00, which is a map for Garmin GPS units and a software for viewing and syncing them with GPS device. The software and maps are old and outdated, but they may still be useful for those who use Garmin GPS devices.

Please seed it, and keep it alive.
